  <li>February 18 (Hermite amphitheater):  <a href="http://www.damtp.cam.ac.uk/user/cbs31/Home.html">Carola Sch√∂nlieb (Cambridge)</a>, <em>From shallow to deep variational models</em>, 9h-12h30 <a href="https://www.dropbox.com/s/fcippohu50b7y1f/Schonlieb_IHPImagingLearningLecturesFeb2019.pdf?dl=0">Slides</a>.</li>
